The paper focuses on improving the search of datasets used in biomedical experiments, which involves information retrieval (IR) techniques such as query expansion and similarity measures. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as word embeddings, which falls under cs.CL. The paper deals with managing research datasets, which involves database (DB) management, making cs.DB another likely sub-category. The paper also uses machine learning (ML) techniques such as dataset categorization, which falls under cs.LG and cs.AI.
